    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the safety and efficacy of elsamitrucin in patients with relapsed or refractory
      non-Hodgkin's lymphoma (NHL). To determine if elsamitrucin is efficacious in a particular
      pathologic NHL subtype(s).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
